title: Apple Streusel Coffee Cake
ingredients: ['325g light brown soft sugar', '100g plain flour', '110g butter, chilled and diced', '2 teaspoons ground cinnamon', '120g chopped walnuts', '400g plain flour', '1 1/2 teaspoons baking powder', '3/4 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '175g butter, room temperature', '300g caster sugar', '3 eggs', '2 teaspoons vanilla extract', '450g plain yogurt', '2 Granny Smith apples - peeled, cored and finely diced']
